  "time_ut": 1658751880,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db4\u0da7 \u0d86\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db0\u0db1\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We are not invited to an all-party government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leaders of Tamil and Muslim political parties said that they have not yet received an official invitation to form an all-party government.",
        "In this regard, when we asked the leader of the All Ceylon People's Congress, Mr. Rishad Badurdeen, he said that such an invitation has not been received yet.",
        "He also mentioned that he saw that such a government would be formed only from the media.",
        "In this regard, in a query made to TNA Media Spokesperson, Member of Parliament MA Sumandhiran, he said that there is no invitation to an all-party government.",
        "He said that he will consider joining such a government after receiving the invitation.",
        "When asked about the formation of an all-party government, the leader of the Tamil Progressive Alliance, MP Mano Ganesan, said that there is no such invitation yet.",
        "He also mentioned that when the leaders of the parliamentary parties met after the swearing in of the President, they informed that such a government would be formed.",
        "In a query made to the leader of the National Labor Front, Member of Parliament Mr. Palani Digambaram regarding the all-party government, he stated that his party has not received such an invitation so far.",
        "He also mentioned that after receiving an invitation, the party will discuss it and take a decision."
      ],
